{"tid":475471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反了！】殖民政府稱不會為故宮項目投放公帑","createTime":"2017-11-21T06:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T06:53:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cb70a8e8b757e89d6970276613d2986908975be6","tid":475471,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T06:53:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1365995-20171121.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1365995-20171121.htm&d=zW8s0yBelm5wq9enpmvRSHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=16a5a0a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1365995-20171121.htm&h=9b9a4a4d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1365995-20171121.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會一個小組委員會開會，議員關注西九文化區故宮文化博物館的管理事宜，以及會否超支。<br />\n<br />\n民政事務局表示，殖民政府不會為故宮項目投放公帑。西九文化區管理局行政總裁栢志高相信，馬會捐出的35億元已足夠，承諾不會超支。"}]}